Various spelling mistakes in comments.
Detected with the help of Coccinelle.

Link: https://lore.kernel.org/all/20220314115354.144023-28-Julia.Lawall@inria.fr
Signed-off-by: Julia Lawall <Julia.Lawall@inria.fr>
